19 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
20 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 441 of Title 72, unless there is
21 created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
22 A. There is hereby authorized the establishment by the Oklahoma
23 Veterans Commission of a private, not-for-profit, charitable
24 organization to be known as the “State of Oklahoma Veterans
